Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked her up on the northern front.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have a name.\NI've just been calling her "you."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't treat a child like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gil, she's no child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a war tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already made arrangements\Nwith the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,LEIDENSCHAFTLICH\NDEPARTMENT OF THE NAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I demand to see\NCaptain Diethard Bougainvillea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, you can't see the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a matter\Nthat requires his confirmation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop asking already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is going on here?\N-Captain! My apologies, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman was demanding to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought,\Nonce a weapon, always a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, tell me!\NIs it true that Major Gilbert
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is missing in action?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert is no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! That's impossible!\NThe major is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you making that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just a tool to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just an emotionless tool,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so, how could you be sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be able\Nto accept the truth now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!\NYou always have the worst timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To top it off, you have no idea\Nabout how women feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go find her already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you draw a bath for her\Nand get her a change of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I tell the madam?\NShe is currently at the mansion in Leiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am just looking after this girl\Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Stop! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master,\NI managed to get her changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but she would not stop struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her to the parlor once she's eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to use a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be cold tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! No! You can't go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,she's been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't even eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot take her to the front lines.\NThe girl is too unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you opposing this?\NThis is an order from the top brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen what she can do\Non the training grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's only good for killing,\Nand completely useless otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take her with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-But--\N-Don't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just exploit this orphaned girl\Nas much as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and dump her in the battlefield\Nwhen she's no longer of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-She isn't ready...\N-That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for your hypocrisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order! You're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:07:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The United Gardarik Army\Nhas begun advancing to Bociaccia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We immediately set up a defensive line\Nalong Bociaccia's capital city of Capria,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and they've now entered\Na war of attrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our forces number 30,000\Nto their 60,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Our forces are holding on, but the enemy\Nbrought cannons to the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Our soldiers' morale\Nhas taken a hit from the bombings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a chance the front will break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-And, so, Major Bougainvillea.\N-Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to lead a company\Nto take out the cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. I will not fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move until I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Major, we are ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Major. An enemy guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact the main battalion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Leidenschaftlich is under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get more soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the enemy is close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the major...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the major here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Young Master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert Bougainvillea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the major's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You should become someone\Nthat matches their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,V...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Violet, and I'm the major.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Major,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Next, let's learn how to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Major, here is my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's well written.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to hand in a daily report\Nto help you practice writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I will submit a daily report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,While we didn't find his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we did find his ID tag
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,under the debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, he was deemed missing in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert is no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This city was occupied\Nby Gardarik forces for three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but they were finally liberated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Thanksgiving tradition\Nhere in Machtig
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to give gifts\Nto those you are thankful to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Tell me something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. If that is your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to express my thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. For all the fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl your age would want\Ndresses or accessories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I wish for\Ndresses and accessories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the same color as your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when I look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful brooch, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of the word\N"beautiful" until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it similar to the word "pretty?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't want one\Nthat matches your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this was the most beautiful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not know the word,\Nwhich is why I've never said it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But your eyes were beautiful\Nfrom the moment we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-The brooch.\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,WESTERN FRONT\NOBERGERG
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,LEIDENSCHAFTLICH ARMY\NFRONT LINE HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gardariks pulled back\Nfrom the west coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we'll be\Nhome by spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's all make it home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel Hodgins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the higher rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange how your blunt attitude\Nseems so endearing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed either.\NEven after becoming a lieutenant colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because they kept sending me\Nto places we could win without fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family is an important\Nfinancier of our military.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't blame headquarters\Nfor keeping you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I don't feel good\Nbeing promoted like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what about you?\NHow have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating enough food?\NI hope you're getting enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can relax, he is only joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be older than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but we were in the same class\Nin officer school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen her\Nat the training ground before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You still had her by your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she the one\Nwho wreaked havoc in Capria?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There are rumors going around\Nthat she's your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You should make her\Ndo something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't have a name,\Nso, I gave her one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you also using her\Nfor Operation Regain Intense?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If this operation succeeds,\Nthe enemy will crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It will likely be the final fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, once this war is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about quitting the army\Nand starting a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A company?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hire you when I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the idea\Nof working under you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess I'll hire Violet instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that might be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huddle up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Do you no longer need me?\N-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After I am dismissed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,will I be transferred to\NLieutenant Colonel Hodgins' command?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I never receive any orders\Nfrom you again, major?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going into battle in a few hours.\NWe can talk about this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's main headquarters\Nis located in Intense, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's surrounded by cliffs,\Nmaking it a natural fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacking from the front\Nwill be too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, our artillery\Nwill bombard the enemy first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,While the enemy is distracted,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll use the sewers\Nto infiltrate Intense,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,rush to the cathedral,\Nand take control of their headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After we do,\Nwe will send up a flare
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to signal our reinforcements\Nto charge, and our operation is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Understood?\N-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes until artillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire artillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire artillery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All squads, report!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad 1 has lost three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad 2 is mostly intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Squads 3 and 4 have lost half our men!\NWe're going to need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squads 1 and 2\Nwill secure the perimeter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and draw the enemy reinforcements in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone left in Squads 3 and 4 will\Ntake control of the cathedral with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go!\N-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Circle right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Major!
